data.description: Welcome home to this 2400 Sq ft 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom house! This house boasts a large master bedroom with private bathroom and walk in closet. The other 3 bedrooms are oversized with large closets. The main floor laundry is conveniently located for easy access. Along with a formal dining room, an inviting family room with a warm woodburning fireplace. This home has abundant storage such as a pantry, linen closets near bathrooms and a large coat closet near the entryway. Basement is currently unfinished but offers great potential. Your new home is located in a great neighborhood with a park and pond for the kids to enjoy. Highly regarded Hononegah school district. Close to shopping, restaurants and easy access to I-90. Water heater installed in October of 2023. Welcome home!
